Kiss on the Road Kisses of Kindness hit the road last Thursday in Partnership with three Naivas Supermarket branches. Kiss FM presenters Kamene and Jalang'o surprised three lucky winners with gift vouchers worth Sh20,000 each. The winners were taken to Naivas Mountain View for breakfast before going for shopping at the branch.Â  Other participating branches were Naivas Buruburu and Naivas Airport View. Branch manager Morris Kiunge was delighted to see the Kiss FM team. "I am so glad that the Kiss FM team chose to visit us today, feel at home and come back again," he said.